\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5
Medzi hlavn\u233\'e9 okruhy t\u233\'e9m upravovan\u253\'fdch n\u225\'e1vrhom z\u225\'e1kona patria spresnenia a doplnenia ustanoven\u237\'ed t\u253\'fdkaj\u250\'facich sa pou\u382\'7e\u237\'edvan\u253\'fdch z\u225\'e1konn\u253\'fdch pojmov, overovania ur\u269\'0den\u253\'fdch meradiel, spotrebite\u318\'3esky balen\u253\'fdch v\u253\'fdrobkov, autoriz\u225\'e1cie, registr\u225\'e1cie skutkov\u253\'fdch podst\u225\'e1t za poru\u353\'61enie z\u225\'e1kona a \u250\'faprava v\u253\'fd\u353\'61ky pok\u250\'fat a v neposlednom rade \u250\'faprava vz\u357\'65ahu k zahrani\u269\'0diu. S\u250\'fa\u269\'0das\u357\'65ou n\u225\'e1vrhu z\u225\'e1kona je n\u225\'e1vrh noveliz\u225\'e1cie z\u225\'e1kona \u269\'0d. 455/1991 Zb. o \u382\'7eivnostenskom podnikan\u237\'ed a z\u225\'e1kona \u269\'0d. 145/1995 Z. z. o spr\u225\'e1vnych poplatkoch. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5
