\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\b\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5
Z. Kramplov\u225\'e1, poslanky\u328\'48a: }{\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5
\u270\'0eakujem za slovo. V\u225\'e1\u382\'7een\u253\'fd p\u225\'e1n minister, v\u225\'e1\u382\'7een\u233\'e9 kolegyne a kolegovia, len v kr\u225\'e1tkosti mo\u382\'7eno nadvia\u382\'7eem na pani poslanky\u328\'48u V\u225\'e1\u353\'61\u225\'e1ryov\u250\'fa. P\u225\'e1n minister, ja v\u225\'e1m gratulujem, \u382\'7ee sa v\u225\'e1m podarilo tento materi\u225\'e1l, tento n\u225\'e1vrh z\u225\'e1kona dosta\u357\'65 do parlamentu a \u382\'7ee m\u225\'e1 t\u250\'fa podobu, ak\u250\'fa m\u225\'e1. Mysl\u237\'edm si, \u382\'7ee t\u225\'e1 podoba, ktor\u225\'e1 moment\u225\'e1lne je, naozaj nebude nikomu prek\u225\'e1\u382\'7ea\u357\'65, aby tento n\u225\'e1vrh nepre\u353\'61iel touto snemov\u328\'48ou, a predpoklad\u225\'e1m, \u382\'7ee d\u225\'e1, pod\u318\'3ea m\u244\'f4jho n\u225\'e1zoru, tak\u253\'fd z\u225\'e1klad pre \u271\'0fal\u353\'61ie fungovanie zahrani\u269\'0dnej slu\u382\'7eby, ktor\u225\'e1 bude ma\u357\'65 oporu v z\u225\'e1kone po prv\u253\'fd raz v hist\u243\'f3rii Slovenskej republiky. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5
Pokia\u318\'3e ide o znenie z\u225\'e1kona, rozm\u253\'fd\u353\'61\u318\'3eala som nad niektor\u253\'fdmi paragrafmi, preto\u382\'7ee tak ako pani poslanky\u328\'48a hovorila o \u167\'a7 17, \u382\'7ee tam nemus\u237\'ed by\u357\'65, ja sa domnievam, \u382\'7ee pr\u225\'e1ve z d\u244\'f4vodu operat\u237\'edvnosti \u167\'a7 5, ktor\u253\'fd hovor\u237\'ed o slu\u382\'7eobnom \u250\'farade. Mysl\u237\'edm druh\u253\'fd odsek, je tam rozp\u237\'edsan\u233\'e9, \u269\'0do maj\u250\'fa obsahova\u357\'65 dokumenty \u8211\'13 rodn\u233\'e9 \u269\'0d\u237\'edsla, adresy a\~podobne. A ob\u225\'e1vam sa toho, \u382\'7ee v pr\u237\'edpade ur\u269\'0ditej nutnosti uv\u225\'e1dza\u357\'65 aj niektor\u233\'e9 in\u233\'e9 veci, ktor\u233\'e9 m\u225\'e1 vies\u357\'65 slu\u382\'7eobn\u253\'fd \u250\'farad, a slu\u382\'7eobn\u253\'fd \u250\'farad m\u225\'e1 pomerne ve\u318\'3ea kompetenci\u237\'ed, \u382\'7ee bude t\u253\'fdm oklie\u353\'61ten\u253\'fd. \u268\'0ci by nebolo rozumnej\u353\'61ie to proste da\u357\'65 do nejakej jednej vety alebo nejak\u233\'e9ho tretieho odseku, v kr\u225\'e1tkosti poveda\u357\'65, o \u269\'0do ide, ale nezv\u228\'e4zova\u357\'65 si ruky priamo vymenovan\u237\'edm, \u269\'0do ten slu\u382\'7eobn\u253\'fd \u250\'farad m\u225\'e1 robi\u357\'65. Budeme to ma\u357\'65 nakoniec v zahrani\u269\'0dnom v\u253\'fdbore, tak\u382\'7ee predpoklad\u225\'e1m, \u382\'7ee to spolo\u269\'0dne  d\u225\'e1me dokopy tak, aby to bolo v poriadku.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5
A e\u353\'61te by som mala jednu tak\u250\'fa pripomienku k \u167\'a7 7. Ten sa t\u253\'fdka diplomatickej misie a st\u225\'e1lej misie. Ja som pozerala t\u250\'fa n\u225\'e1pl\u328\'48, ktor\u225\'e1 je pri diplomatickej misii, a rozm\u253\'fd\u353\'61\u318\'3eala som, \u382\'7ee ke\u271\'0f\u382\'7ee tam m\u225\'e1te v\~ods. 1 p\u237\'edsm. h) uveden\u250\'fa aj koordin\u225\'e1ciu humanit\u225\'e1rnej pomoci, \u269\'0di by sme tam nevedeli zakomponova\u357\'65 aj ofici\u225\'e1lnu rozvojov\u250\'fa pomoc. Dobre viete, \u382\'7ee je to tak\u225\'e1 moja srdcov\u225\'e1 z\u225\'e1le\u382\'7eitos\u357\'65. Navrhovala som to v tej jednej novele, \u269\'0di by jednou vetou tam nebolo mo\u382\'7en\u233\'e9 vsun\u250\'fa\u357\'65 aj ofici\u225\'e1lnu rozvojov\u250\'fa pomoc, lebo bude to jedna z ve\u318\'3emi d\u244\'f4le\u382\'7eit\u253\'fdch oblast\u237\'ed zahrani\u269\'0dnej slu\u382\'7eby a zahrani\u269\'0dnej politiky Slovenskej republiky. \u268\'0ci\u382\'7ee mysl\u237\'edm si, \u382\'7ee by sa tam dalo doplni\u357\'65. Ale znovu pr\u237\'eddem aj s n\u225\'e1vrhom v zahrani\u269\'0dnom v\u253\'fdbore. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5
A m\u225\'e1m jednu ot\u225\'e1zo\u269\'0dku na v\u225\'e1s. Pri slu\u382\'7eobnom \u250\'farade je to \u167\'a7 5. Tam sa dost\u225\'e1va pojem sprev\u225\'e1dzaj\u250\'faca osoba. Je tam defin\u237\'edcia, \u382\'7ee teda je to man\u382\'7eel a die\u357\'65a. Chcem sa op\u253\'fdta\u357\'65, ke\u271\'0f je to druh a dru\u382\'7eka alebo nie\u269\'0do in\u233\'e9, nem\u244\'f4\u382\'7ee by\u357\'65 sprev\u225\'e1dzaj\u250\'faca osoba? Nem\u225\'e1me myslie\u357\'65 teraz u\u382\'7e aj na to, ke\u271\'0f\u382\'7ee to d\u225\'e1vame do z\u225\'e1kona, preto\u382\'7ee vieme, ako sa tieto soci\u225\'e1lne stavy vyv\u237\'edjaj\u250\'fa. A mysl\u237\'edm, \u382\'7ee vy to ve\u318\'3emi dobre viete aj na ministerstve. Ve\u318\'3emi pekne \u271\'0fakujem a samozrejme, \u382\'7ee podpor\u237\'edm tento n\u225\'e1vrh.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5

\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\b\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5
M. Hort, podpredseda NR SR: }{\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5
\u270\'0eakujem. Ani na pani poslanky\u328\'48u Kramplov\u250\'fa nie s\u250\'fa \u382\'7eiadne faktick\u233\'e9 pozn\u225\'e1mky, a preto m\u225\'e1 slovo teraz v rozprave posledn\u253\'fd prihl\u225\'e1sen\u253\'fd p\u225\'e1n poslanec Juraj Horv\u225\'e1th. Nech sa p\u225\'e1\u269\'0di.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5

\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\b\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5
J. Horv\u225\'e1th, poslanec: }{\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5
V\u225\'e1\u382\'7een\u233\'e9 d\u225\'e1my, v\u225\'e1\u382\'7een\u237\'ed p\u225\'e1ni, som r\u225\'e1d, \u382\'7ee m\u244\'f4\u382\'7eeme znovu na p\u244\'f4de parlamentu, najvy\u353\'61\u353\'61ieho z\u225\'e1konodarn\u233\'e9ho zboru na Slovensku rokova\u357\'65 o z\u225\'e1kone o zahrani\u269\'0dnej slu\u382\'7ebe. Je to v porad\u237\'ed druh\u253\'fd z\u225\'e1kon, ktor\u253\'fd m\u225\'e1me v tomto volebnom obdob\u237\'ed na stoloch po z\u225\'e1kone o rozvojovej pomoci, ktor\u253\'fd som mal \u269\'0des\u357\'65 spravodajcova\u357\'65, ktor\u253\'fd priniesol tie\u382\'7e nov\u233\'e9 modern\u233\'e9 prostriedky v\u253\'fdkonu diplomacie v\~zahrani\u269\'0d\u237\'ed. Tak teraz prich\u225\'e1dza tento z\u225\'e1kon o zahrani\u269\'0dnej slu\u382\'7ebe, som r\u225\'e1d z mnoh\u253\'fdch d\u244\'f4vodov. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5
Prv\u253\'fd, samozrejme, k\u318\'3e\u250\'fa\u269\'0dov\u253\'fd d\u244\'f4vod je, \u382\'7ee tento z\u225\'e1kon pom\u225\'e1ha stabilizova\u357\'65 pomery na ministerstve zahrani\u269\'0dn\u253\'fdch vec\u237\'ed, pom\u225\'e1ha stabilizova\u357\'65 mechanizmus fungovania. Rovnako som pote\u353\'61en\u253\'fd t\u253\'fdmto aj preto, \u382\'7ee za posledn\u233\'e9 roky, a t\u253\'fdch rokov naozaj ubehlo ve\u318\'3ea, nebolo mo\u382\'7en\u233\'e9 z politick\u253\'fdch d\u244\'f4vodov a mo\u382\'7eno aj odborn\u253\'fdch d\u244\'f4vodov prija\u357\'65 tak\u253\'fdto z\u225\'e1kon. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5
Pokia\u318\'3e viem, naposledy zablokoval ten z\u225\'e1kon Ivan Miklo\u353\'61, ktor\u253\'fd v poslednej chv\u237\'edli zablokoval v\u353\'61etko, \u269\'0do sa pripravilo. Preto aj z tohto d\u244\'f4vodu som r\u225\'e1d, \u382\'7ee som po\u269\'0dul od pani poslankyne, pani kolegyne V\u225\'e1\u353\'61\u225\'e1ryovej, \u382\'7ee je pripraven\u225\'e1 podpori\u357\'65 tento z\u225\'e1kon, \u382\'7ee tomu m\u244\'f4\u382\'7eem rozumie\u357\'65 asi tak, \u382\'7ee aj cel\u225\'e1 SDK\u218\'da podpor\u237\'ed tento z\u225\'e1kon. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5
Rovnako v tejto chv\u237\'edli dod\u225\'e1vam, \u382\'7ee tento z\u225\'e1kon je tak\u253\'fd d\u244\'f4le\u382\'7eit\u253\'fd, \u382\'7ee ho podpor\u237\'ed strana SMER \u8211\'13 soci\u225\'e1lna demokracia a po dohode s koali\u269\'0dn\u253\'fdmi partnermi o\u269\'0dak\u225\'e1vame u\u382\'7e, prirodzene, aj podporu koali\u269\'0dn\u253\'fdch partnerov pri hlasovan\u237\'ed. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5
Mo\u382\'7eno zd\u244\'f4razn\u237\'edm v prvom \u269\'0d\u237\'edtan\u237\'ed len jeden moment v tomto z\u225\'e1kone a ostatn\u233\'e9 si asi nech\u225\'e1me v\u353\'61etci re\u269\'0dn\u237\'edci na druh\u233\'e9 \u269\'0d\u237\'edtanie. A to ten moment, v\u225\'e1\u382\'7een\u237\'ed p\u225\'e1ni poslanci, panie poslankyne, v\u225\'e1\u382\'7een\u253\'fd p\u225\'e1n minister, \u382\'7ee sme mali dlhodob\u253\'fd probl\u233\'e9m na ministerstve zahrani\u269\'0dn\u253\'fdch vec\u237\'ed s vysielan\u237\'edm diplomatov, ktor\u253\'fdch sprev\u225\'e1dzaj\u250\'faci bl\u237\'edzki mali probl\u233\'e9m sprev\u225\'e1dza\u357\'65 t\u253\'fdchto diplomatov z obavy o svoje d\u244\'f4chodkov\u233\'e9, zdravotn\u233\'e9 zabezpe\u269\'0denie, jednoducho o soci\u225\'e1lnu dimenziu, ktor\u225\'e1 je pre nich ve\u318\'3emi d\u244\'f4le\u382\'7eit\u225\'e1. Toto \u269\'0dasto sp\u244\'f4sobovalo, \u382\'7ee diplomati uva\u382\'7eovali nad t\u253\'fdm, \u382\'7ee opustia vysielaj\u250\'facu krajinu a p\u244\'f4jdu do miesta ur\u269\'0denia do krajiny prij\u237\'edmaj\u250\'facej bez man\u382\'7eelky, bez man\u382\'7eela, \u269\'0do, samozrejme, sp\u244\'f4sobuje bezpe\u269\'0dnostn\u233\'e9 rizik\u225\'e1. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5
Vieme ve\u318\'3emi dobre, \u382\'7ee v diplomacii v ka\u382\'7edom \u353\'61t\u225\'e1te s\u250\'fa ist\u233\'e9 nep\u237\'edsan\u233\'e9 pravidl\u225\'e1, ktor\u233\'e9 treba dodr\u382\'7eiava\u357\'65, a pr\u225\'e1ve tieto sme my  poru\u353\'61ovali a\~\u269\'0dasto poru\u353\'61ujeme. A pr\u225\'e1ve tento z\u225\'e1kon m\u225\'e1 stabilizova\u357\'65 pomery na ministerstve zahrani\u269\'0dn\u253\'fdch vec\u237\'ed tak, aby sme sa mohli vyh\u253\'fdba\u357\'65 poru\u353\'61ovaniu t\u253\'fdchto pravidiel, ktor\u233\'e9 potom sp\u244\'f4sobuje zvy\u353\'61ovanie bezpe\u269\'0dnostn\u253\'fdch riz\u237\'edk. Toto je k\u318\'3e\u250\'fa\u269\'0dov\u253\'fd moment, ktor\u253\'fd som chcel v prvom \u269\'0d\u237\'edtan\u237\'ed zd\u244\'f4razni\u357\'65 a ver\u237\'edm tomu, \u382\'7ee budeme m\u244\'f4c\u357\'65 o tom viacej hovori\u357\'65 v druhom \u269\'0d\u237\'edtan\u237\'ed. Preto mi dovo\u318\'3ete za\u382\'7eela\u357\'65 tomuto z\u225\'e1konu hladk\u253\'fd postup do druh\u233\'e9ho \u269\'0d\u237\'edtania a obraciam sa na v\u353\'61etk\u253\'fdch, ktor\u237\'ed s\u250\'fa v parlamente, aby podporili tento z\u225\'e1kon. \u270\'0eakujem pekne.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5

\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\b\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5
M. Hort, podpredseda NR SR: }{\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5
\u270\'0eakujem. S faktickou pozn\u225\'e1mkou na vyst\u250\'fapenie p\u225\'e1na poslanca Horv\u225\'e1tha sa prihl\u225\'e1sila pani Magdal\u233\'e9na V\u225\'e1\u353\'61\u225\'e1ryov\u225\'e1 ako jedin\u225\'e1. Uzatv\u225\'e1ram mo\u382\'7enos\u357\'65 prihl\u225\'e1si\u357\'65 sa s faktickou pozn\u225\'e1mkou a slovo m\u225\'e1 pani V\u225\'e1\u353\'61\u225\'e1ryov\u225\'e1. Nech sa p\u225\'e1\u269\'0di.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5

\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\b\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5
