Za\u269\'0dnem asi u posledn\u233\'e9ho. Asi ste reagovali tesne ved\u318\'3ea, ke\u271\'0f ste hovorili o vl\u225\'e1de Vladim\u237\'edra Me\u269\'0diara. Ja som ju ani slovkom nespomenul, ale to je u\u382\'7e vec \u8222\'1etrafen\u253\'fdch hus\u237\'ed\u8220\'1c alebo proste rie\u353\'61en\u237\'ed, ktor\u233\'e9 v\u225\'e1m robia probl\u233\'e9my. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5
K ochrane spotrebite\u318\'3ea, ktor\u250\'fa ste spom\u237\'ednali. \u193\'c1no, treba chr\u225\'e1ni\u357\'65 aj spotrebite\u318\'3eov, treba chr\u225\'e1ni\u357\'65 aj na\u353\'61ich dod\u225\'e1vate\u318\'3eov. Ja pozn\u225\'e1m na\u353\'61ich v\u253\'fdrobcov niektor\u253\'fdch potrav\u237\'edn, ktor\u237\'ed s\u250\'fa schopn\u237\'ed sa prebojov\u225\'e1va\u357\'65 a prebojov\u225\'e1vaj\u250\'fa sa tak, \u382\'7ee pon\u250\'fakaj\u250\'fa dobr\u233\'e9 v\u253\'fdrobky, pon\u250\'fakaj\u250\'fa konkurencieschopn\u250\'fa cenu, a dokonca si buduj\u250\'fa vlastn\u250\'fa obchodn\u250\'fa sie\u357\'65. A robia to preto, lebo nechc\u250\'fa d\u225\'e1va\u357\'65 svoje v\u253\'fdrobky do t\u253\'fdchto re\u357\'65azcov a nechc\u250\'fa ich d\u225\'e1va\u357\'65 pri ve\u318\'3ek\u253\'fdch tlakoch a s\u250\'fa schopn\u237\'ed existova\u357\'65. Ke\u271\'0f nebudeme ma\u357\'65 tak\u253\'fdchto dod\u225\'e1vate\u318\'3eov a v\u253\'fdrobcov, na \u269\'0dom budeme stava\u357\'65, pros\u237\'edm v\u225\'e1s pekne? Iba na tom, \u382\'7ee budeme st\u225\'e1le d\u225\'e1va\u357\'65 nejak\u233\'e9 dot\u225\'e1cie, o ktor\u253\'fdch nikto nebude vedie\u357\'65, kam tie dot\u225\'e1cie vlastne id\u250\'fa? }
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5
Je norm\u225\'e1lnym sp\u244\'f4sobom tak\u233\'e9 fungovanie, \u382\'7ee st\u225\'e1le ako s t\u253\'fdm pravidlom, \u382\'7ee d\u225\'e1m ti chlieb, d\u225\'e1m ti rybu a d\u225\'e1m ti jedlo a ty bude\u353\'61 ako\u382\'7ee m\u225\'e1rni\u357\'65 v\u353\'61etko, jedno za druh\u253\'fdm, alebo d\u225\'e1m ti udicu a nau\u269\'0d sa chyta\u357\'65 ryby, aj ich chytaj. A aj ten dod\u225\'e1vate\u318\'3e nem\u225\'e1 to jednoduch\u233\'e9, ale mus\u237\'ed by\u357\'65 schopn\u253\'fd sa prebojova\u357\'65 v r\u225\'e1mci t\u253\'fdchto podmienok trhu tak, aby bol schopn\u253\'fd pre\u382\'7ei\u357\'65. Ke\u271\'0f toto nedosiahneme, tak potom darmo budeme rozpr\u225\'e1va\u357\'65 o slovensk\u253\'fdch dod\u225\'e1vate\u318\'3eoch, o slovensk\u253\'fdch v\u253\'fdrobcoch. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\langfe1033\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\lang1051\loch\f5
\u270\'0eakujem aj za podporu kolegovi Simonovi, ale mysl\u237\'edm si, \u382\'7ee tak\u233\'e9to zn\u225\'e1sil\u328\'48ovanie rie\u353\'61en\u237\'ed a hlavne v takej frekvencii, v akej ju rob\u237\'edte, \u382\'7ee neust\u225\'e1le nie\u269\'0do novelizujeme, tak si mysl\u237\'edm, \u382\'7ee toto nem\u244\'f4\u382\'7ee prinies\u357\'65 dobr\u233\'e9 rie\u353\'61enie. Bohu\u382\'7eia\u318\'3e, tak\u233\'e9to veci sa robia ve\u318\'3emi \u269\'0dasto v tomto parlamente.}
